{
  "texts": [
    "Initially, we will briefly overview the dataset used, implementation details, and evaluation metrics.",
    "Subsequently, we will compare and analyze the experimental results of our model with those of other state-of-the-art models.",
    "Additionally, we conducted ablation experiments to explore the roles of various components in the proposed model.",
    "Finally, we will discuss the potential application value of this model in content fusion and the restoration of complex degraded images in real-world environments.",
    "Datasets: In the case of face super-resolution (8×), the same training data as SR3 22 is utilized, consisting of 70,000 images from FFHQ 37 and 28,000 images from CelebA-HQ 27."
  ]
}